---
source: src/cli/mod.rs
assertion: curate tombstone writes audit record without deleting memory row
schema:
  response: ee.response.v1
  tombstone: ee.curate.tombstone.v1
contracts:
  - tombstone writes an audited record without deleting the memory
  - dry-run preview reports what would be tombstoned
  - missing memory returns NotFound with repair hint
  - actor recorded in audit metadata when provided
  - reason recorded in audit trail
  - JSON stdout is ee.response.v1 envelope
  - exit code 6 when degraded mode unavailable
evidence:
  - CurateTombstoneArgs.memory_id
  - CurateTombstoneArgs.dry_run
  - CurateTombstoneArgs.actor
  - CurateTombstoneArgs.reason
  - DomainError::UnsatisfiedDegradedMode
